SCHEMA: time/compaction_policy.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.time.compaction_policy
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic save/log compaction policy rows.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record compaction_policy
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - compaction_policy_id: id
    - rules: map
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Compaction rules must preserve replayability from retained checkpoints.
- Compaction is deterministic and non-semantic.
